Class SimpleComplexNumber

  • Object
    • AbstractComplexNumber<BigInteger,SimpleComplexNumber,RealComplexNumber,BigIntMatrix>
      • SimpleComplexNumber
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MathNumber<SimpleComplexNumber,RealComplexNumber,BigDecimal>

    @Beta
public final class SimpleComplexNumber
extends AbstractComplexNumber<BigInteger,SimpleComplexNumber,RealComplexNumber,BigIntMatrix>
    An immutable implementation of a complex number which uses BigInteger as type for its real and imaginary part
